<add><ab facs="#facs_420_r2l14">vnd yeglich </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>ın</expan> kawffleẅt vnd auch furleẅt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l16">von <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / dıe yecʒunt in der vaſtenmeſſe ʒu frankfurt ſeyn . wıſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l17">daʒ wir Anthonij Derrer <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> lıeben <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen . 
