<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l24">vnd faren ſüllet 
<add><ab facs="#facs_420_r1l2">darinn wır Jn </ab><ab facs="#facs_420_r1l3"><expan>vnſer<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_420_r1l4">wol <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>rıchtet</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_420_r1l5">haben </ab></add> / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>heıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gepıet<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch allen vnd </ab>
