<ab facs="#facs_420_r2l27">ſelbs <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd eẅr hab vnd <expan>kawffmanſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> ſchıken </ab>
