<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l4">Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Judıca </ab>
